---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Header />

  <section class="bg-white">
    <div
      class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-12 md:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-16"
    >
      <div class="md:w-4/5">
        <h1 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-fuchsia-600">
          Contact Us
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-3xl">
          We&apos;re here to help with every order.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          At RMVS Market, we value open communication and are always here to assist
          our customers. If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback regarding
          our products, orders, payments, deliveries, or services, please feel free
          to reach out to us through the contact details provided below.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
        <p>
          Our customer support team is dedicated to responding promptly and
          professionally to all inquiries. Whether you need help with order
          tracking, billing information, returns, or general assistance, we are
          committed to ensuring a smooth and satisfactory experience for every
          customer.
        </p>
        <p>
          You may contact us via phone or email during our business hours, and we
          strive to address all requests as quickly as possible. Your trust and
          satisfaction are important to us, and your feedback helps us improve our
          services and offerings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        id="contact"
        class="mt-10 grid gap-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/60 p-6 text-sm text-slate-800 md:grid-cols-2 md:p-8"
      >
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">
            Company Name
          </h2>
          <p>
            RMVS SALES AND MARKETING PRIVATE LIMITED
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">
            Address
          </h2>
          <p>
            Shop A-01 s.no.2 Euriska, Nr New Delhi School, Mohamadwadi, Pune
            City, Pune-411060, Maharashtra
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">
            Phone
          </h2>
          <p>
            +91 9310492477
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500">
            Email
          </h2>
          <p>
            rmvscare@gmail.com
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

